name: NYDailyNews
text:
Two wounded Bronx teens caught in an early-morning shooting aren't talking about who shot them or what happened.

The teens refused to tell investigators what occurred prior to the shooting and were “combative” when asked about happened.

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Liberty rookie Megan Walker tested positive for coronavirus.

The UConn product will miss the start of training camp, but the team is hopeful she’ll recover and make her WNBA debut once it is safe for her to do so.
https://t.co/6V84PaCSCg

name: NYDailyNews
text:
The NHL and the NHL players’ union approve a plan to resume the season.

The return-to-play plan was ratified by the league’s board of governors and with majority approval from players following a three-day voting period.
https://t.co/ub1j52Qc1J
